      <title>美联储降息步伐放缓 市政债券涨幅创 5 月以来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/municipal-bonds-rally-most-since-may-as-fed-seen-slow-to-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者担心美联储等待太长时间才降息，市政债券普遍上涨，收益率创七周以来最大降幅，纷纷放弃股票，转而投资固定收益资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/municipal-bonds-rally-most-since-may-as-fed-seen-slow-to-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 19:18:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
